:0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:13:41.000Z","msg":"頭先食飯隔離圍檯坐咗班廢老大大聲屌政府<br />\n不停鬧陳茂波冇撚用做埋d弱智野<br />\n之後又鬧出嚟遊行嗰一百萬人係住公屋拎綜援嘅廢青<br />\n冇野做先會出嚟搞事<br />\n坐監係因為搵唔到野做冇錢所以坐監呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬧完一輪又鬧朱凱迪張超雄係仆街仔<br />\n跟住又繼續鬧而家嘅政府全部都係冚家產<br />\n<br />\n真係相信魯迅d文一千年後都仲用得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6945629b2b91db3087247bbec8e608bdd427a53","tid":1275176,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:37:20.000Z","msg":"《人生的意義》- 殷海光<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1277375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1277375</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n覺得學術台可以開始做啟蒙活動<br />\n教導各位點解要抗爭"},{"pid":"5702ef5cfadcb8244db7992b264ff75d6f36961c","tid":1275176,"uid":132256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:24:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2327f6995300d92ee50200912e170419101f1b82","tid":1275176,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:54:42.000Z","msg":"呢篇文好有啟發作用<br />\n1.奴才（深藍廢老）係有破壞無建設既垃圾<br />\n唔好再試圖爭取奴才既民意<br />\n2.傻子有勇但無謀 砸牆係好 但要幪面同識走 咁先唔會比人捉 可以長期抗爭"},{"pid":"cc3e224465975a6f69751fade7746a33c3a42e34","tid":1275176,"uid":106641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f15f2d194c60e02100cdae655a207f8a0b9e04f7","tid":1275176,"uid":9962,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:24:33.000Z","msg":"呢一百年嚟，中國人係冇進步過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:56:15.000Z","msg":"唔係一百年嚟，係幾千年嚟都冇，劣根性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca69fefaa71a1d3ae856168cfa2bb0d33e5d90dd","tid":1275176,"uid":9962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc3e224465975a6f69751fade7746a33c3a42e34","tid":1275176,"uid":106641,"like